<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n18113k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n18" href="#n18113k">N18 (VI.B.8)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n18all.htm#n18113k"> 113(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> basterna (<font color="green">[bang]</font>) </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: BASTERNA: a kind of litter (<i>lectica</i>) in which women were carried at the time of the Roman emperors. It appears to have resembled the lectica very closely; and the only difference apparently was that the lectica was carried by slaves and the basterna by two mules.</mm> </dd></dl>
